@startuml
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #ffffff
  BorderColor black
  Style roundrect
}
left to right direction

rectangle "GitHub Repository" as GitHub
rectangle "Analysis Service" as Analysis
rectangle "Gemini API" as Gemini
rectangle "Error Handler" as ErrorHandler
rectangle "Retry Logic" as Retry
rectangle "Quota Monitor" as QuotaMonitor

GitHub --> Analysis : Process content
Analysis --> Gemini : API Request
Gemini --> Analysis : 429 Error (Rate Limit Exceeded)
Analysis --> ErrorHandler : Handle error
ErrorHandler --> Retry : Trigger retry with backoff
Retry --> Gemini : Retry request
ErrorHandler --> QuotaMonitor : Track usage
QuotaMonitor --> Analysis : Adjust chunk size
@enduml